        "text": "As I i can't edit my original message to this thread I want to put in here some context.\n\nCONTEXT:\n\nThe Butlerian Jihad is a Conecpt from Dune: <https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Dune:_The_Butlerian_Jihad>\n\nIt invokes for me the conecept of a quite drastical discourse with Technology, espedially AI.",
